Fake Britain: Series 7
Series which reveals the extent of fake goods in the UK, and investigates the conmen who are trying to get their hands on your money.



4)  Part 4 
Matt Allwright investigates the fake hoverboards catching fire in people's homes, the counterfeit designer jackets that are deceiving consumers and making thousands for the fakers, and the sophisticated silver copies of high street jewellery which contain no silver at all.
